## 🚀 Going Live

To switch to **Live Mode**:
1. Complete KYC on Razorpay dashboard
2. Get **Live API Keys** (start with `rzp_live_`)
3. Update `.env` with live keys
4. Test thoroughly before going live

---

## 💡 Notes

- Free classes (price = 0) skip payment
- Paid classes require Razorpay payment
- All transactions are recorded in Payment model
- Admin users cannot enroll in classes

